      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and it truly lives up to that description. The exterior is virtually flawless \u2014 the paint retains its deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, or swirl marks, and all body panels are perfectly aligned with no signs of prior accident damage or bodywork. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new with no tears, stains, or significant wear on the seats, carpets, or trim surfaces. Mechanically, this car is in excellent shape \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and cleanly, all systems function as intended, and it has been well-maintained throughout its life. Tires have strong tread remaining, brakes are in great condition, and there are no warning lights or known issues. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally cared for and is ready to impress from the moment you take the wheel.",
