    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a well-maintained used car that has been cared for and is ready for its next owner. The exterior presents nicely, showing only minor surface wear and small scuffs consistent with normal everyday use; nothing that detracts significantly from its overall appearance. The paint retains good color and gloss, and the body panels are straight without any major dents or damage. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional, with upholstery showing moderate wear on the high-contact areas such as the driver's seat and door panels, but no tears or significant staining. All primary controls, electronics, and comfort features are in working order. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, the transmission shifts smoothly, and it handles as expected for a used car of this age and mileage. Routine maintenance has been kept up, and there are no outstanding mechanical concerns at this time. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged. This is a solid, dependable used car offered honestly and priced fairly for its condition.",
